State-owned enterprises and advantageous private enterprises enter the old revolutionary area of Gannan.
From September 26th to 27th, in order to deepen the educational achievements of "never forget the original intention and remember the mission" theme, the Central Military-civilian Integration Office, the National Defense Science and Industry Administration, and the National Federation of Industry and Commerce jointly organized the research activities of "State-owned Enterprises and Advantage Private Enterprises Entering the Old District of the Gannan Revolution", revisited the history of the revolution, traced the red footprint, passed on the red gene, carried out the demand docking between relevant enterprises and the city of Ganzhou, and promoted the development of the old revolutionary area.
Jin Zhuanglong, executive deputy director of the Central Military-civilian Integration Office, Xu Lejiang, vice minister of the Central United Front, secretary of the party group of the National Federation of Industry and Commerce, executive vice chairman Xu Lejiang, director of the National Defense Science and Industry Bureau Zhang Kejian, deputy secretary of the Jiangxi Provincial Party Committee, and secretary of the Ganzhou Municipal Party Committee Li Bingjun participated in the investigation.
