Ctrip reported that the per capita cost of inter-provincial tourism per capita during the National Day holiday is more than 3000 yuan, which is due to the fact that tourists generally choose to experience better products, such as high-scoring brand hotels, no shopping tours, exquisite small groups, special car specials and so on.
