China's development path, in line with China's national conditions, adapts to the requirements of the times, will increasingly show bright development prospects as the times progress.
In view of the international community's concern for China's development, the white paper emphasizes that the realization of national prosperity, national rejuvenation and people's happiness is both the dream of the Chinese people and the common dream of the people of all countries.
The white paper pointed out that China is the main stabilizer and power source of world economic growth, and China's opening up to the outside world creates more opportunities for the development of all countries, China provides more public goods for the international community, China's development provides experience and reference for other developing countries, and China will never take the road of "national strength must be overbearing."
