Fujian Provincial Tax Bank Financial Comprehensive Tax Payer Platform is officially launched.
China New Network Fuzhou September 27th (Yeqiuyun) Fujian Provincial Tax Bank convenient people's comprehensive tax payment platform was officially launched on September 27th in Fuzhou City, Fujian Province.
The reporter learned that on October 26, 2018, the Fuzhou Central Branch of the People's Bank of China, together with the Fujian Provincial Taxation Bureau of the State Administration of Taxation and China UnionPay Co., Ltd., jointly signed a memorandum of cooperation, and created a comprehensive tax payment platform for Fujian Provincial Tax Bank in the country.
After nearly a year of construction, the platform has been successfully launched.
Wang Dehui, director of the State Treasury Department of Fuzhou Center Branch of the People's Bank of China, introduced that the platform upholds the concept of security, versatility, convenience, compliance and leading construction, and connects the front-end tax, government, banking, non-bank payment institutions and social service parties, and provides a variety of online and offline tax payment channels such as mobile APP, WeChat public number, tax hall, bank outlets, and inclusive financial service points.
It is reported that the platform brings together a number of projects for the benefit of the people, among them, the urban and rural residents' medical insurance payment project has been officially launched.
The project has opened up 14 channels online and offline to provide services to more than 30 million urban and rural residents in Fujian Province, covering 76% of the permanent resident population of Fujian Province.
Medical insurance fees can be paid online through "Miner Tax" and "Cloud Flash Payment" and the APPs of various banks and WeChat public numbers; offline can be paid in various ways such as scanning code, waving, and card-brushing in Fujian Province through various ways.
The deputy governor of the Fuzhou Central Branch of the People's Bank of China said that the success of the platform is on the line, while ensuring the direct payment of government income into the library and the real-time interaction of data information, it can provide a safe and efficient, multi-channel and multi-mode convenient tax payment service for the public.
At present, more than 16000 inclusive financial service points in the province, more than 9000 have opened the medical insurance payment function, so that rural residents can "not leave the village" can safely investigate the medical insurance fee, so that the public has a stronger sense of "acquiet" and "happiness".
According to statistics, since the 20th of the pre-trial operation of the urban and rural residents' medical insurance payment project, the service users have reached 84 million, of which the online payment users have reached 75 million, and the number of users paid by the inclusive financial services point is nearly twenty thousand times.
In addition, Lin Gueros, deputy director of the Fujian Provincial Taxation Bureau of the State Administration of Taxation, revealed at the event that the platform has pioneered the application of blockchain electronic payment voucher technology in the country.
Starting next month, the contributor can also download the stamping stamp directly through the mobile phone after the payment is completed, the payment person can also download the stamped electronic payment voucher.
The Fujian tax information network based on blockchain technology is being built, and the "highway" of convenient private tax payment will be further broadened.
