New regulations for consultation: social capital to obtain rural land management rights need to be qualified
Social capital to obtain rural land management rights must be qualified
The Measures for the Management of Rural Land Management Rights shall be publicly solicited for comments, and the social capital transfer such as industrial and commercial enterprises shall be regulated for land management rights
Yesterday, the website of the Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Affairs issued a notice on the Measures for the Management of Rural Land Management Rights (Draft for Comment) (hereinafter referred to as the "Draft Opinions"), which increased the supervision and risk prevention of the right to land management of industrial and commercial enterprises and other social capital transfer.
The draft opinion is now open to the public for comments.
The Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Affairs said that in order to implement the newly revised Rural Land Contracting Law, further consolidate and improve the basic rural management system, deepen the reform of the rural land system, and implement the "separation of three rights" system, the Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Affairs has revised the Measures for the Management of Rural Land Contract Management Rights and Management, and formed the "Professional Opinions".
Beijing Youth Daily reporter learned that the "Opinions Draft" published for the first time has many important changes.
The newly revised Rural Land Contracting Law clarifies the scope of land transfer, implements the concept of "separation of three rights", and sets up "land contract management rights" and "land management rights", respectively, and makes a clear distinction between the transfer, exchange and transfer of land management rights (rent, subcontracting, equity or other means).
In this "Draft Opinions", in order to implement the concept of "separation of three rights", effectively respond to the essence of the revision of the "Rural Land Contracting Law", taking into account the transfer of land management rights and land contract management rights swap, transfer in the parties, procedures, supervision and other aspects of the big difference, the draft of this revision of the scope of circulation, focusing on the land management rights of land management, including leasing, equity, etc.
For the transfer and exchange of land contract management rights, the management measures will be issued separately.
The "Professor" pointed out that in the context of "separation of powers", farmers' equity is only a land management right for a certain period of time.
In theory, even in the event of bankruptcy liquidation, the farmer only has the risk of losing the right to operate for a certain period of time, so it is not necessarily in principle that the return of the contract to the original contractor is no longer necessary and there is a conflict with the Bankruptcy Law.
In view of the problem of preventing the risk of landlessness of farmers, in practice, there are methods such as preferred stocks, first rent and then stocks, and repurchases.
Taking into account the fact that preferred stocks already have more mature theoretical discussions in the company law, it is recommended to use it as an advocacy provision to prevent the risk of loss of shares.
